Media Query
-----------
1. Media query is mainly used to make web page responsive.
2. We need to use @media key to implement media query in our website.
3. We can make web page responsive on various width and orientation.Here width can be 360px, 450px, 540px, 920px etc and orientation includes portrait and landscape.
4. syntax : 

@media screen | all | print | speech and (max-width:360px | min-width:450px | orientation : portrait or landscape){
    .....
}

@media screen and (max-width:360px){
    .....
}

@media all and (min-width:450px){
    .....
}

@media screen and (orientation : portrait){
    .....
}

@media screen and (orientation : landscape){
    .....
}

@media screen and (min-width:360px) and (max-width:720px){
    .....
}
